{"tid":899233,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴︰曼聯唔會降班","createTime":"2018-11-12T09:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T17:00:40.000Z","uid":37875,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a768c0c6d8518c79a119d877be9313e0debc7f44","tid":899233,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:25:05.000Z","msg":"曼城3：1輕取曼聯 阿古路平曼市打吡入球紀錄<br />\n<br />\n紅魔在比賽以1︰3落敗後，於聯賽榜已落後曼城12分，爭標機會甚微，不過他幽默地說︰「我想我們不會降班，曼城開季至今一直狀態大勇，而我們開季不好但不斷改善中。」<br />\n<br />\n「比賽直至80分鐘仍然充滿變數，我想曼城射入第3球前沒有球迷會離場。今個星期曼城3場都是主場賽事，當中包括大勝6︰0可輕鬆比賽。但我們是3場作客，而對祖雲達斯就像決賽一樣，對心理和體力的要求很高。」<br />\n<br />\nNEW RECORD <br />\n<br />\nThis is the first time in English top-flight history that 3 clubs have remained unbeaten in their opening 12 games of the season (Man City, Liverpool, Chelsea) <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/BXkUeL3H0c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FBXkUeL3H0c&d=F77gZwdEA7vBqSzj0okTBwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=abee2bee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/BXkUeL3H0c</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash; Premier League (@premierleague) November 11, 2018<br />\n「所以不懂足球的人會看數字，但我只會看自己感受，我認為球隊今場只犯了一次錯誤，但表現不是很差，不論身心都很好，戰鬥至最後一刻，不會因為輸波而否定一切。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=F77gZwdEA7vBqSzj0okTBwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=5be46c41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://更多Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9AGoal.com&d=F77gZwdEA7vBqSzj0okTBwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=6ad3f746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">更多Goal.com</a>內容, 請按此"},{"pid":"6bc9b0aa8ef2e12e2be06a50b0d7fb2d3cb260b9","tid":899233,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"17弟?"},{"pid":"e522b3daf2030693dfecf3e95810785932a6ddc5","tid":899233,"uid":33601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:28:37.000Z","msg":"總之我地曼聯仍然不敗"},{"pid":"68b7481b156e2bb0ac5e795d09a279f280644fe1","tid":899233,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bc9b0aa8ef2e12e2be06a50b0d7fb2d3cb260b9","tid":899233,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"17弟?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:33:17.000Z","msg":"尊重"},{"pid":"166bb20da9a194848a2fdab81d9780221f2e6d97","tid":899233,"uid":6577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:38:54.000Z","msg":"洗7億都降班摩狗應該冇命行出奧脫福"},{"pid":"14c7c9e93bbb695c15445c0c5887f5887468b8d7","tid":899233,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:09:28.000Z","msg":"降左班仲邊有野笑"},{"pid":"82377b4b84646af4a0a700b4d79b94b207f54818","tid":899233,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T16:57:03.000Z","msg":"難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b792a889b95621ee9e3ec0e0780fda8a7bde82","tid":899233,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T17:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}